23:10.630 --> 23:12.762
- Ah, we've got lots of rooms.

23:15.866 --> 23:17.503
I give you
the best one.

23:18.198 --> 23:20.396
- Looks to be kind of quiet
around here.

23:20.431 --> 23:21.936
- You know, we have this town.

23:21.971 --> 23:23.971
People still come here
to gamble.

23:24.512 --> 23:26.677
Tiberio Vargas
y<i> sus hombres,</i>

23:26.712 --> 23:28.580
they come here, they gamble.

23:28.615 --> 23:31.407
We still have<i> rucas.</i>
<i>Buenas rucas.</i>

23:31.442 --> 23:34.487
We have the house dealer,
Sylvio, an honest man.

23:35.281 --> 23:37.985
- Right now, that's just
what the doctor ordered.

23:38.020 --> 23:40.460
Gonna suit me right down
to the ground.

23:41.155 --> 23:43.595
Joe Cribbens,
at your service.

23:43.630 --> 23:46.356
-<i> Entonces...</i> What,
you are a businessman?

23:46.391 --> 23:51.031
- I retired. I just like
to play cards and...

